-- Ace Names McBride To Head of International Claims, Replacing Day
-- B y   S t e v e n   N o r t o n
-- 2012-06-25T21:35:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-25/ace-names-mcbride-to-head-of-international-claims-replacing-day.html
Ace Ltd. (ACE) , the Zurich-based insurer
with operations in more than 50 nations, named Andrew McBride as
executive vice president for claims in its international
business effective today.  He replaces Roger Day, who will retire from the company at
the end of the year, the insurer said today in a statement
distributed by Business Wire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Steven Norton in New York at 
 snorton7@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
